u8strings (0.1.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Improve the build system:
    + Set default PREFIX and DESTDIR.
    + Add “test-installed” target.
    + Add checks against BSD make.
      (Only GNU make is supported.)
  * Improve the test suite:
    + Don't hardcode the Perl interpreter path in script shebang;
      use “#!/usr/bin/env perl” instead.

 -- Jakub Wilk <jwilk@jwilk.net>  Tue, 19 Feb 2019 20:46:21 +0100

u8strings (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix synopsis in the manual page.
  * Improve the build system:
    + Add “install” target.
    + Add “test” target.
    + Don't use getconf(1) to acquire LFS build flags.
  * Automatically enable American Fuzzy Lop deferred forkserver.
  * Put license into a separate file.

 -- Jakub Wilk <jwilk@jwilk.net>  Thu, 09 Nov 2017 21:33:07 +0100

